com.viaoa.web.html

Class HtmlElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.web.html.HtmlElement
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    HtmlCol, HtmlColGroup, HtmlDiv, HtmlFormElement, HtmlImg, HtmlLink, HtmlScrollPanel, HtmlTable, HtmlTD, HtmlTR, OAAccordionBar, OAHtmlElement, OATable, OATree, OAVisibleObserverElement

    public class HtmlElement
extends Object
    Base class for all HTML Elements.

    This uses an internal OAHtmlComponent, and overwrites some of it's public methods to call protected methods in this class (for method "hiding").
